{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_15", "eventName": "解離重組", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "15-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "執此劍者", "storyInfo": "特雷西斯進入內化宇宙對抗源石中的意志。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "50_g19_babeltop_ex2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$faceoff_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）新的冗餘資訊？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡剩下的，也只有虛無？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他看著那個菱形，就像——"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……盯著我的眼睛。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#4$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特雷西斯生平第一次，有了戰慄的感覺。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那並非來自他本能的反應，他感知到，一種他無法觸碰的意志試圖迫使他屈服——"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_bladeline_01_large", "rox": 60.0, "roy": 20.0, "roz": 50.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神明也罷，造物主也罷，直面我。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死寂，冰冷。虛無中，並無一物，也並無回應。"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，你不應該來這裡。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "殿下已經犯下了魯莽的錯誤。我不想再次失去我在乎的人，老師。", "name": "“阿斯卡綸”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開吧，老師，時機尚未成熟。", "name": "“阿斯卡綸”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不應該用她來侮辱我，自詡的造物主。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前的阿斯卡綸絕非幻影，這處奇妙的空間將他的記憶化為了實體。"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在我的記憶中，依舊還是過去的樣子，稚嫩了一點。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#8$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？", "name": "“阿斯卡綸”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然真正掌控這裡的那些人不敢直面我，說明特蕾西婭的確成功了。他們必然已經受到了諸多的限制。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則那些傲慢的存在也不至於試圖讓你阻止我。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特雷西斯舉起了劍。"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師，你還是不願意跟我離開？", "name": "“阿斯卡綸”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰勝我，如果你真的想將我帶走。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "“阿斯卡綸”"}, "figure_art": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$knifegore"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_02_s", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_spark_01_large", "layer": 3.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "afrom": 0.0, "rfrom": 0.0, "gfrom": 0.0, "bfrom": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_skill_skulsrsword", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$swordtsing4", "delay": 0.1}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_bladeline_01_large", "roy": 20.0, "roz": 292.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "focus": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,0"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很熟練，但依舊只是我教你的技巧。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4132_ascln_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.1, "r": 0.2, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.5, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“阿斯卡綸”的身形隱入了紫色的霧氣之中，那是屬於她的源石技藝。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特雷西斯想起了他與特蕾西婭帶領薩卡茲的殘軍走入風暴中的那天……"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他隻身走入紫色的煙霧之中，抓住了那個孩子手中的刀。一如此刻。"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1297_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好久不見，阿斯卡綸。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1297_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}